This is how to install playwright in command palette.
go to view> command palette> type "install playwright" check the javascipt.

Use this command in powershell to install or make it unrestricted.

1. Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser
2. Set-ExecutionPolicy Unrestricted -Scope CurrentUser
3. Get-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser

To revert the policy: Set-ExecutionPolicy Restricted -Scope CurrentUser

<<Testing>> 
npx playwright test ///default
npx playwright test --headed ///shows testing process
npx playwright test HomePageTest.spec.js --project=chromium ///Using specific browser
npx playwright test HomePageTest.spec.js ///run specific file
npx playwright test HomePageTest.spec.js --debug ///manual step by step execution
